一、作業說明

此次作業為文字雲，將爬蟲抓下來的資料，經過文本清理列成字頻矩陣後，繪製成文字雲。



二、批踢踢爬版

最初爬的是表特版（Beauty），但出現太多無意義的文字或類似的推文。所以換了和樂家庭版（FamilyCircle）和媽寶版（BabyMother），想看看大家的家庭困擾都是哪些？畢竟家家有本難念的經，但大家的煩腦換成文字大宗就是「爸爸、媽媽、寶寶、親戚」等指稱性代名詞看也看不出什麼。所以最後選了Salary版，看看大家對於工作上的討論大概都是些什麼？ 



library(tmcn)
## # tmcn Version: 0.1-4
rm(list=ls(all.names = TRUE))
library(rvest)
## Loading required package: xml2
#install.packages("tmcn", 
#repos="http://R-Forge.R-project.org")


URL   = "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Salary/index.html"
html  = read_html(URL)
title = html_nodes(html, "a")
href  = html_attr(title, "href")
data = data.frame(title = toUTF8(html_text(title)),
                     href = href)
data = data[-c(1:10),]
getContent <- function(x) {
  url  = paste0("https://www.ptt.cc", x)
  tag  = html_node(read_html(url), 'div#main-content.bbs-screen.bbs-content')
  text = toUTF8(html_text(tag))
}

#getContent(data$href[1])
allText = sapply(data$href, getContent)
write.table(allText, "mydata.txt")



三、文本清理

rm(list=ls(all.names = TRUE))
library(NLP)
library(tm)
library(jiebaRD)
library(jiebaR)
library(RColorBrewer)
library(wordcloud)
filenames <- list.files(getwd(), pattern="*.txt")
files <- lapply(filenames, readLines)
docs <- Corpus(VectorSource(files))

#移除可能有問題的符號
toSpace <- content_transformer(function(x, pattern) {
  return (gsub(pattern, " ", x))})

docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "※")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "◆")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "‧")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "的")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "我")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "是")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "看板")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "標題")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "文章")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "作者")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "發信站")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "批踢踢實業坊")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "[a-zA-Z]")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "噓")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "推")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "→")


docs <- tm_map(docs, removePunctuation)
docs <- tm_map(docs, removeNumbers)
docs <- tm_map(docs, stripWhitespace)
docs
## <<SimpleCorpus>>
## Metadata:  corpus specific: 1, document level (indexed): 0
## Content:  documents: 1



四、詞頻矩陣

mixseg = worker()
jieba_tokenizer=function(d){
  unlist(segment(d[[1]],mixseg))
}
seg = lapply(docs, jieba_tokenizer)
freqFrame = as.data.frame(table(unlist(seg)))
freqFrame = freqFrame[order(freqFrame$Freq,decreasing=TRUE), ]


freqFrame = as.matrix(freqFrame)
for (i in 1:dim(freqFrame)[1]){
  freqFrame[i,1] <- as.character(freqFrame[i,1])
  if(nchar(freqFrame[i,1]) == 1){
    freqFrame[i,2] <- 0}}

freqFrame1 <- freqFrame
freqFrame1 <- as.data.frame(freqFrame1)
temp = which(freqFrame1$Freq != 0)
a1 <- as.character(freqFrame1$Var1[temp])
b1 <- freqFrame1$Freq[temp]
freqFrame2 <- as.data.frame(cbind(a1, b1))
colnames(freqFrame2) <- c("var", "freq")


freqFrame30 <- freqFrame2
freqFrame30 = as.matrix(freqFrame30)
for (i in 1:dim(freqFrame30)[1]){
  freqFrame30[i,1] <- as.character(freqFrame30[i,1])
  if(nchar(freqFrame30[i,1]) == 2){
    freqFrame30[i,2] <- 0}}

freqFrame31 <- freqFrame30
freqFrame31 <- as.data.frame(freqFrame31)
temp1 = which(freqFrame31$freq != 0)
a2 <- as.character(freqFrame31$var[temp1])
b2 <- freqFrame31$freq[temp1]
freqFrame3 <- as.data.frame(cbind(a2, b2))
colnames(freqFrame3) <- c("var", "freq")

library(knitr)
kable(head(freqFrame2), format = "markdown")

五、文字雲

a11 <- as.character(a1)
b11 <- as.integer(b1)

# mac要補這行才不會無法顯示，下載字型（細黑體）。
par(family=("Heiti TC Light"))
cloud2 <- wordcloud(a11,b11,
          scale=c(5,0.1),min.freq=50,max.words=150,
          random.order=TRUE, random.color=FALSE, 
          rot.per=.1, colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2"),
          ordered.colors=FALSE,use.r.layout=FALSE,
          fixed.asp=TRUE)
